data.description: Beautiful home in Linden’s Byram Ridge subdivision in immaculate condition! This home has everything; square footage, finishings, location, Linden schools, low maintenance, and a wonderful floor plan. Built in 2020 and updated after construction by sellers with security, fixtures, landscaping, and lighting. Master suite with master bath. Gourmet kitchen with granite and pantry. First floor laundry. High efficiency furnace. Certified resnet home. Smart home equippeed with Alexa. Walking trails. Less than 5 minutes from US-23 and Owen Rd and within 5-10 minutes of shopping and all of the award winning restaurants our community has to offer. This house has it all! Schedule your appointment today! Open house Saturday 2/17 from 1pm - 3pm. Interior photos to be uploaded Thursday 2/15. *Listing contract contingent upon sellers finding satisfactory housing. Commission to be paid on net sales price.
